parameters:
Phantom Thief Perno: Haa...haa... Finally made it this
far... Just a little more... Just a little further and I'll
be done--

Noble Skiros: That's as far as you go, Phantom Thief Perno!
I'll make you regret entering my mansion!

Noble Skiros: The honor of my once prestigious family, who
were renowned priests, has been tarnished by the plundering
of Perno...

Phantom Thief Perno: I've made it this far... I'm sorry,
everyone... I'm sorry... Father...
Noble Skiros: Now, capture that person--
Clea: As I thought, this hand is the best.
Thief Nora: Yes! I'm skilled at breaking walls!

Mage Relm: This goes against my sense of beauty! But still,
how were you able to move at that timing?

Priestess Sophia: Hehe, I've been hit by the same magic
before, so it was a close call, but I'm glad I was able to
resist it with my magical power.
Phantom Thief Perno (I really... met some good kids)

Phantom Thief Perno: I can't give you interest, but I'll
return Deirei's left eye!

Security Guard: Phantom Thief Perno is not here!? Could it
be that there were multiple people? I will immediately
initiate pursuit!

Noble Skiros: Beautiful... Did you see that back? Compared
to that, those pebbles over there have no value.

Noble Skiros: Deliver the request letter to Oros
immediately.

Security Guard: Understood! I will gather information on
Phantom Thief Perno!

Noble Skiros: I don't care about such things! Deirei's left
eye has returned, my request is separate.

Noble Skiros: We must find the accomplice of the Phantom
Thief Perno, the one with that beautiful back...!
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Noble Skiros: I want to make you the final subject of
today's examination, now that night has come.
Thief Nora: What should I do then...?
Thief Nora: I-Is this some kind of ritual?

Noble Skiros: To be honest, I haven't even seen the face of
a thief, let alone a collaborator.
Noble Skiros: However! I have been shown something amazing!

Noble Skiros: Your height is quite close to the image,
but... hmmm.

Noble Skiros: I have an idea! Would you mind changing into
thief-like attire?
Noble Skiros: Please, try to remember something!
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
Noble Skiros: Oh! It's quite close to the image!
Noble Skiros: Y-Yes! Show me your back at that place...!
Thief Nora: S-Sorry... I'm scared... ugh
Noble Skiros: Tell me, what is your wish...?

Thief Nora: I would like to withdraw the request to find a
collaborator for the phantom thief.

Thief Nora: There are many people who are troubled by
that...

Noble Skiros: As you have done wrong to the people of Oros,
I will withdraw the request as you wish.
Thief Nora: T-Thank you very much!

Noble Skiros: This is not something a gentleman should do,
but I have a condition for withdrawing the request. I want
you to cooperate with me.

Noble Skiros: Whether you are the collaborator of the
phantom thief or not doesn't matter to me. I have fallen in
love with your personality, your body, and above all, your
back.

Thief Nora: Y-Yes, I understand. If it will save the people
of Oros...
Would you like to skip the adult scene?
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
Noble Skiros: Hmm... Something doesn't quite click...
Do you want to skip the adult scene?
Noble Skiros: Thank you for coming today as well.

Noble Skiros: Now, I would like you to accompany me for a
walk at night.
